    slug: 'midjourney-prompts-master-guide',
    title: 'The Master Guide to Midjourney Prompts in 2026',
    excerpt: 'Master Midjourney prompts with a clear visual framework, current parameters, image and style references, iteration methods, and practical prompt examples.',
    category: 'Midjourney',
